tacts/emergency-contacts/","scope":"state","source_url":"https://www.telangana.gov.in/contacts/emergency-contacts/","source_name":"Telangana State Portal - Emergency Contacts","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15"},{"kind":"url","topic":"grievance","label":"Prajavani - Telangana public grievance portal (Praja Bhavan)","value":"https://prajavani.cgg.gov.in/","scope":"state","source_url":"https://prajavani.cgg.gov.in/","source_name":"Prajavani - Praja Bhavan, Government of Telangana (Centre for Good Governance)","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"CURRENT portal. IMPORTANT: the older Prajavani portal at cpgrams.ts.nic.in was DISCONTINUED per Letter No. 16/Plg/Prajavani/2026 dated 01/06/2026 by the State Nodal Officer for Prajavani - do not link that old URL. Grievances also accepted in person at Mahatma Jyothiba Phule Praja Bhavan, Punjagutta, Hyderabad on Tuesdays and Fridays. Support email: support.prajavani@cgg.gov.in. No helpline number is published on the portal."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"general","label":"MeeSeva Call Centre (citizen services)","value":"1100","scope":"state","source_url":"https://www.telangana.gov.in/contacts/emergency-contacts/","source_name":"Telangana State Portal - Emergency Contacts","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Telangana's 1100 is the MeeSeva citizen-services call centre - it is NOT a CM helpline. Telangana publishes no CM helpline number (confirmed absent from both the state emergency-contacts page and the CMO contact page)."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"general","label":"MeeSeva Call Centre (toll-free)","value":"18004251110","scope":"state","source_url":"https://www.telangana.gov.in/contacts/emergency-contacts/","source_name":"Telangana State Portal - Emergency Contacts","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15"},{"kind":"phone","topic":"general","label":"Chief Minister's Office, Telangana Secretariat","value":"04024422666","scope":"state","source_url":"https://cm.telangana.gov.in/contact/","source_name":"Chief Minister of Telangana - Contact","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"CMO office landline (Dr. B.R. Ambedkar Telangana Secretariat, 6th Floor, Hyderabad 500022). This is an office line, NOT a citizen helpline - label it as such. Alternate: 040-24422999."},{"kind":"url","topic":"police","label":"Telangana State Police - citizen services portal","value":"https://tspolice.gov.in/","scope":"state","source_url":"https://tspolice.gov.in/","source_name":"Telangana State Police - Official Website","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Live and current (DGP message dated May 2026, gallery entries July 2026). Offers lodge/check petition, view FIR, missing persons, arrest particulars, passport status, eChallan status, CEIR portal. Note the domain is still tspolice.gov.in, not tgpolice - tgpolice.cgg.gov.in is an internal police HRMS, not a citizen portal."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"police","label":"Police control room","value":"100","scope":"state","source_url":"https://www.telangana.gov.in/contacts/emergency-contacts/","source_name":"Telangana State Portal - Emergency Contacts","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15"},{"kind":"phone","topic":"police","label":"Crime Stopper","value":"1090","scope":"state","source_url":"https://www.telangana.gov.in/contacts/emergency-contacts/","source_name":"Telangana State Portal - Emergency Contacts","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15"},{"kind":"phone","topic":"ambulance","label":"Ambulance","value":"108","scope":"state","source_url":"https://www.telangana.gov.in/contacts/emergency-contacts/","source_name":"Telangana State Portal - Emergency Contacts","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"State emergency-contacts page also lists 102 for ambulance."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"health","label":"Blood Bank","value":"04024745243","scope":"state","source_url":"https://www.telangana.gov.in/contacts/emergency-contacts/","source_name":"Telangana State Portal - Emergency Contacts","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15"},{"kind":"url","topic":"women","label":"Telangana Police Women Safety Wing (SHE Teams, Bharosa centres)","value":"https://womensafetywing.telangana.gov.in/","scope":"state","source_url":"https://womensafetywing.telangana.gov.in/","source_name":"Women Safety Wing, Telangana Police","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"State-specific women's safety body. Site offers 'Get help by location' and 'Get help by issue' to reach district SHE Teams / Bharosa centres."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"women","label":"Telangana Police Women Safety Wing (phone / WhatsApp)","value":"8712656858","scope":"state","source_url":"https://womensafetywing.telangana.gov.in/contact-us/","source_name":"Women Safety Wing, Telangana Police - Contact Us","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"State-specific Telangana number, reachable by call and WhatsApp. Included in preference to the national 181/1098, which Telangana republishes but does not operate as state-specific lines."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"women","label":"Women Safety Wing office (Lakdikapul, Hyderabad)","value":"04027852246","scope":"state","source_url":"https://womensafetywing.telangana.gov.in/contact-us/","source_name":"Women Safety Wing, Telangana Police - Contact Us","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15"},{"kind":"phone","topic":"electricity","label":"Electricity complaint (statewide, both DISCOMs)","value":"1912","scope":"state","source_url":"https://www.telangana.gov.in/contacts/emergency-contacts/","source_name":"Telangana State Portal - Emergency Contacts","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Published centrally by the state portal and by TGSPDCL; TGNPDCL also uses 1912.","operator":"TGSPDCL & TGNPDCL (1912)"},{"kind":"url","topic":"electricity","label":"TGSPDCL - Southern Power Distribution Co. of Telangana (consumer contact)","value":"https://tgsouthernpower.org/contact","scope":"state","source_url":"https://tgsouthernpower.org/contact","source_name":"TGSPDCL - Contact Us (official DISCOM site)","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Serves Hyderabad and southern Telangana districts. Toll-free 1912; email customerservice@tgsouthernpower.org.","operator":"TGSPDCL","districts":["Hyderabad","Mahbubnagar","Medak","Nalgonda","Rangareddy"]},{"kind":"email","topic":"electricity","label":"TGSPDCL customer service email","value":"customerservice@tgsouthernpower.org","scope":"state","operator":"TGSPDCL","districts":["Hyderabad","Mahbubnagar","Medak","Nalgonda","Rangareddy"],"source_url":"https://tgsouthernpower.org/contact","source_name":"TGSPDCL official contact page","retrieved_date":"2026-07-16"},{"kind":"url","topic":"electricity","label":"TGNPDCL - Northern Power Distribution Co. of Telangana","value":"https://tgnpdcl.com/","scope":"state","source_url":"https://tgnpdcl.com/","source_name":"TGNPDCL - Official DISCOM site","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Serves northern Telangana districts (Warangal, Karimnagar, Nizamabad, Khammam etc.).","operator":"TGNPDCL","districts":["Adilabad","Karimnagar","Khammam","Nizamabad","Warangal"]},{"kind":"phone","topic":"electricity","label":"TGNPDCL supply complaints (toll-free, northern Telangana)","value":"18004250028","scope":"state","source_url":"https://tgnpdcl.com/","source_name":"TGNPDCL - Official DISCOM site","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Published as '18004250028 (or) 1912 (24/7)' for supply-related complaints.","operator":"TGNPDCL","districts":["Adilabad","Karimnagar","Khammam","Nizamabad","Warangal"]},{"kind":"phone","topic":"emergency","label":"National Emergency Number (ERSS) - Police, Fire & Rescue, Health","value":"112","scope":"national","source_url":"https://www.mha.gov.in/en/commoncontent/emergency-response-support-system-erss","source_name":"Ministry of Home Affairs, Government of India","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"MHA's single pan-India emergency number: 'ONE INDIA ONE EMERGENCY NUMBER 112', a nationwide unified emergency response system. Works in every State/UT. Corroborated by india.gov.in helpline directory, which lists 112 as the Integrated Helpline (ERSS) covering Police, Fire & Rescue and Health services."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"fire","label":"Fire Helpline","value":"101","scope":"national","source_url":"https://www.india.gov.in/directory/helpline","source_name":"National Portal of India (india.gov.in), NIC / MeitY","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Listed under 'Emergency Numbers' on the National Portal of India helpline directory (page last reviewed/updated 14 July 2026)."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"ambulance","label":"National Ambulance Service (NAS)","value":"102","scope":"national","source_url":"https://www.india.gov.in/directory/helpline","source_name":"National Portal of India (india.gov.in), NIC / MeitY","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Listed as 'National Ambulance Service (NAS)' under Emergency Numbers on the National Portal of India helpline directory (page last reviewed/updated 14 July 2026)."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"women","label":"Women Helpline (national, toll-free)","value":"181","scope":"national","source_url":"https://wcd.gov.in/","source_name":"Ministry of Women and Child Development, Government of India","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Published as 'Women Helpline Toll free No. - 181' directly by the owning ministry (WCD) as a tel: link on its homepage. Also listed on india.gov.in as both 'Women Helpline Number' and 'Domestic Violence Helpline'."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"women","label":"National Commission for Women (NCW) 24x7 Helpline","value":"14490","scope":"national","source_url":"https://ncw.gov.in/","source_name":"National Commission for Women (NCW)","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"NCW's own site states: 'Call the 24x7 NCW helpline at 14490 for immediate assistance and support', and lists 'NCW Women Helpline (14490)' under its Complaint Redressal cells. IMPORTANT: the india.gov.in helpline directory still lists 7827170170 as the 'National Commission for Women Helpline' - that number appears nowhere on ncw.gov.in (not even in raw HTML), so it appears stale and was deliberately omitted in favour of the department's own current number."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"child","label":"Child Helpline (national, toll-free)","value":"1098","scope":"national","source_url":"https://wcd.gov.in/","source_name":"Ministry of Women and Child Development, Government of India","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Published as 'Child Helpline Toll free No. - 1098' directly by the owning ministry (WCD) as a tel: link on its homepage. Also listed as 'Child Help Line' on india.gov.in."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"senior","label":"Elderline - National Helpline for Senior Citizens (NHSC)","value":"14567","scope":"national","source_url":"https://scw.dosje.gov.in/elderline","source_name":"Department of Social Justice & Empowerment, Government of India","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Published as 'Elder Helpline: 14567' on the Department of Social Justice & Empowerment's own Elderline site, which the ministry homepage links to as the 'National Helpline for Senior Citizens (NHSC)'. india.gov.in additionally lists a landline 011-20893999 alongside 14567 for the Senior Citizens Helpline."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"grievance","label":"National Consumer Helpline (NCH)","value":"1915","scope":"national","source_url":"https://www.india.gov.in/directory/helpline","source_name":"National Portal of India (india.gov.in), NIC / MeitY","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Listed as 'National Consumer Helpline (NCH)' on the National Portal of India helpline directory (page last reviewed/updated 14 July 2026). Note: the NCH portal consumerhelpline.gov.in could not be reached at time of research (DNS resolves to an NIC address but the host refused connections / returned 504), so only the number is cited here - not the NCH portal URL."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"cyber","label":"Cyber Crime Helpline (online financial fraud reporting)","value":"1930","scope":"national","source_url":"https://cybercrime.gov.in/","source_name":"National Cyber Crime Reporting Portal, MHA / I4C","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Confirmed on the National Cyber Crime Reporting Portal homepage banner (MHA / Indian Cyber Crime Coordination Centre - I4C), which reads: 'To report online financial fraud, call 1930' and 'register your complaint at cybercrime.gov.in'. Independently corroborated by the india.gov.in helpline directory, which lists 1930 as the Cyber Crime Helpline."},{"kind":"url","topic":"cyber","label":"National Cyber Crime Reporting Portal (file a cybercrime complaint)","value":"https://cybercrime.gov.in/","scope":"national","source_url":"https://cybercrime.gov.in/","source_name":"National Cyber Crime Reporting Portal, MHA / I4C","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Verified live. Ministry of Home Affairs portal for reporting cybercrime; supports anonymous reporting, women/children-related crime, financial fraud and other cybercrime, plus complaint tracking. Nationwide."},{"kind":"url","topic":"grievance","label":"CPGRAMS - Centralised Public Grievance Redress and Monitoring System","value":"https://pgportal.gov.in/","scope":"national","source_url":"https://pgportal.gov.in/","source_name":"Ministry of Personnel, Public Grievances & Pensions, Government of India","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Verified live; this is the citizen-facing portal. The site states CPGRAMS is 'an online platform available to the citizens 24x7 to lodge their grievances to the public authorities on any subject related to service delivery... a single portal connected to all the Ministries/Departments of Government of India and States.' Supports tracking by registration ID and an appeal facility. Note: it does not cover RTI matters, subjudice/court matters, or religious matters."},{"kind":"url","topic":"corruption","label":"Central Vigilance Commission - lodge a corruption complaint","value":"https://portal.cvc.gov.in/","scope":"national","source_url":"https://portal.cvc.gov.in/","source_name":"Central Vigilance Commission (CVC), Government of India","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Verified live. CVC's Complaint Management System with a 'Citizen Login', complaint status tracking and a published complaint handling policy. Linked from cvc.gov.in as 'Lodge a complaint'. Covers corruption complaints against central government organisations."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"disaster","label":"Relief Commissioner for Natural Calamities","value":"1070","scope":"national","source_url":"https://www.india.gov.in/directory/helpline","source_name":"National Portal of India (india.gov.in), NIC / MeitY","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Listed on the National Portal of India helpline directory (page last reviewed/updated 14 July 2026)."},{"kind":"phone","topic":"road","label":"Road Accident Helpline","value":"1073","scope":"national","source_url":"https://www.india.gov.in/directory/helpline","source_name":"National Portal of India (india.gov.in), NIC / MeitY","retrieved_date":"2026-07-15","note":"Listed on the National Portal of India helpline directory (page last reviewed/updated 14 July 2026)."}]}